<p style="font-size: 16px;">Hello <strong><%= @resource.email %></strong>,</p>

<p style="font-size: 15px;">
  A request has been received to reset the password for your account. You can reset your password by clicking the button below:
</p>

<p>
  <%= link_to 'Change My Password', edit_password_url(@resource, reset_password_token: @token),
      style: "display: inline-block; padding: 10px 20px; background-color: #0d6efd; color: #fff;
              text-decoration: none; border-radius: 5px; font-weight: bold;" %>
</p>

<p style="font-size: 14px;">
  If you did not request this change, you can safely ignore this email. Your password will remain unchanged unless you use the link above to set a new one.
</p>
